	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hit GreaterFayMart and buy some bronze or banded. Just save up...We all had to start from scratch. After level 20 or so you need to start concentrating on wisdom more than AC. They're both very important but you'll find yourself going OOM more than is acceptable in many groups. Luckily there is a plethora of armor out there with both stats on it so you won't have to give up much in either department to realize your true effectiveness.<br>&nbsp;<br>"You want proof of Brell's power? The proof is in the bottle, the higher the proof the better!"</td></tr>
