	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cleric quest armor pieces are:<br><br>Chestplate of the Constant <br>Vambraces of the Fervent <br>Greaves of the Pentient <br>Boots of the Reliant (easiest piece)<br>Bracers of the Reverent (best piece)<br>Gauntlets of the Ardent <br><br>Those are all the cleric quest pieces (I can think of).  Some are fairly easy to do, and can be done as soon as you are ready to venture into the world (Boots).  Others I suggest doing with friends when level 30+ (Chest and Bracer mainly). <br><br>On a side note, two easy pieces for most clerics out there.  <br>Adamantite Epolets (fairly cheap, good AC and +wis for cleric)<br>Bloodstained Tunic (get around 300pp and good AC and +wis for clerics)<br><br>Hope this helps you!!<br><br>E-mail: Tekkie78@hotmail.com<br>&nbsp;<br>Draggun<br>Cleric of Brell - The Nameless</td></tr>
