	   <tr><td colspan=2>Worry not.  Alakhazam's can provide you with many good maps to guide you to unrest.  If you're on the west side of Kithicor, see if oyu can get a generous druid to port you from Karana to Butcherblock.  From there, you just have to cross Dagnor's Cauldron to get to Unrest.  Not an easy path, true.  <br><br>But if you can get a port, consider making Freeport your home for the next few levels.  At lever 14, and as a cleric, you will have no problem finding groups in east and west commons, N ro, and Oasis.  And if you have a need to kill lots of undead, organize a Befallen expadition.  All these zones are very close to Freeport.<br><br>If you're in Freeport, shame on you.  Get a map and take the boat to Butcherblock.<br><br>If you need other advice, look my cleric up sometime.  Her tag's Slymbia.<br>&nbsp;<br>Alerithon Tigerspirit<br>29 rank monk, E'Ci<br>Avatara</td></tr>
